OL,5, Menopause symptoms can be considered a 
OL,6, disability and employers face being    
OL,7, sued if they do not make "reasonable   
OL,8, adjustments", a watchdog has said.     
OL,10,FThe Equality and Human Rights          
OL,11,FCommission (EHRC) issued the guidance  
OL,12,Fto clarify the legal obligations to    
OL,13,Fworkers going through the menopause.   
OL,15,FSymptoms can include hot flushes, brain
OL,16,Ffog and difficulty sleeping.           
OL,18,FThe EHRC said bosses should offer      
OL,19,Fchanges such as providing rest areas or
OL,20,Fflexible hours to help.                
